✨ 65 Years, 3 Generations, 10 Women, 1 Legacy ✨ 
A story woven through time, told by the incredible women of Aristocrat’s founding family. From the eldest to the youngest, they share memories, style & the timeless elegance that defines 65 years of styling generations.

Join us as we celebrate this journey & unveil the Spring Summer Collection’25 for women at our exclusive Pop-Up Event!
21st & 22nd March📍Aristocrat Galaxy, Pakhowal Road, Ludhiana 

A legacy stitched with love, waiting to be a part of your story. See you there! 💫
